# Backend routing (Option B)

- Prefer adding new endpoints in `backend/routes/*.py` using `APIRouter`.
- Ensure `backend/main.py` includes the router(s) so endpoints are reachable under `/api/v1/...`.
- Avoid duplicating endpoints between `main.py` and `routes/*`.

